text: Judy is a soundtrack by Renée Zellweger for the film of the same name. It was released on September 28, 2019, by Decca Records. The album features songs performed by Zellweger in character as Judy Garland from the film along with duets with Sam Smith and Rufus Wainwright. ==Track listing== ==Charts== {| class="wikitable plainrowheaders" style="text-align:center" |- ! scope="col"| Chart (2019) ! scope="col"| Peak position |- |} ==References== Category:2019 soundtrack albums Category:Decca Records soundtracks Category:Judy Garland tribute albums
